Similarly you can get the[LC Name Authority record for Herman Melville](http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n79006936) from the Internet Archive using the RDFa that is embedded embedded in the page:

import rdflib

g = rdflib.Graph()
url = "http://web.archive.org/web/20130614192231/http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n79006936.html"
g.parse(url, format="rdfa")
print g.serialize(format="turtle")

