## Hacking O'Reilly RDFa

December 22, 2009   
[rdfa](https://inkdroid.org/2009/12/22/hacking-oreilly-rdfa/tag/rdfa) [identifiers](https://inkdroid.org/2009/12/22/hacking-oreilly-rdfa/tag/identifiers) [linked-data](https://inkdroid.org/2009/12/22/hacking-oreilly-rdfa/tag/linked-data) [oreilly](https://inkdroid.org/2009/12/22/hacking-oreilly-rdfa/tag/oreilly) [graphs](https://inkdroid.org/2009/12/22/hacking-oreilly-rdfa/tag/graphs) 

